{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "曲徑求勝", "storyInfo": "騎行環節，鼠膽龍威隊遭到了進一步針對，不得已進入巷道，卻依然被包圍。\n埃內斯托讓陳林二人進入自己武器店，自己留下斷後。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨著比賽的進行，先頭部隊已經通過了騎行檢查點，而就在這時，比賽也迎來了一些變化！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在第一輪比賽中大顯神威的鼠膽龍威隊，在通過了騎行檢查點並騎上了車後，立刻就遭到了其他隊伍的重點照顧。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，這一次他們似乎改變了策略。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坎黛拉女士，能否請您為大家講解一下！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不明擺著嗎，這幫人知道自己就算一起上也未必是這支隊伍的對手，於是選擇拖住他們的腳步，而不是打敗他們。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跑步環節即使用這種方法也很容易被這兩人近身，但是騎行階段，在車上很多招式不好施展。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以他們選擇在騎行環節這麼做。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不得不說，效果不錯。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實，他們緊緊跟在鼠膽龍威隊附近，不上前進攻，只用各種手段進行騷擾，讓鼠膽龍威隊無法安心地趕路。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們看到，鼠膽龍威隊現在已經落後先頭部隊許多了！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "騎在車上施展不開，而下車只會落後！鼠膽龍威隊，面臨著比賽開始以來最大的危機！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G03"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的目的不是打敗我們，是拖住我們。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼辦，兩位，騎行中戰鬥是很困難的，這樣下去我們要被完全拖住了。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）看來，有人想讓我們抄近道。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）我知道。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）闖一闖？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）呵。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#7"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了擺脫阻礙自己的其他隊伍選手，鼠膽龍威隊選擇了插入巷道之中！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，正如我們在別的舞台所看到的，在巷道中，等待著我們的選手的，是這座城市的精銳部隊！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我也想為各位講解其他隊伍的視角，但是鼠膽龍威隊實在是太吸引人注目了！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鼠膽龍威隊此舉究竟是自尋死路，還是險中求勝，讓我們拭目以待！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G02"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "fadetime": 0.3}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，走這邊！這條巷子很隱秘，我估計沒人......", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當心。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 4.0, "ystrength": 4.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 30.0, "fadeout": "false"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_arrow_h"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.